1. Crear el entorno virtual (Python venv)
cd mi_proyecto
python3 -m venv env

2. Activar el entorno virtual
source env/bin/activate

3. Instalar dependencias desde requirements.txt
pip install -r requirements.txt

4. Borrar env 
rm -rf venv

execute Augmentation:
python3 src/Augmentation.py "../leaves/images/Apple_Black_rot/image (23).JPG"

execute Transformation:
image input:
python3 ./src/Transformation.py -src "../leaves/images/Apple/Apple_Black_rot/image (110).JPG" -dst "new" 
python3 ./src/Transformation.py -src "../leaves/images/Apple/Apple_Black_rot/image (110).JPG" -f negative

directory input:
python3 ./src/Transformation.py -src "../leaves/images/Apple/Apple_Black_rot"